<lyrics>[V1]
 Sevaman, sevaman,
 chin yurakdan sevaman Isoni
 Sevaman, sevaman,
 chin yurakdan sevaman
 Sevasizmi Isoni
 chin yuraginizdan ?
 Ha, sevamiz, Isoni biz yuragimizdan.</lyrics>
<title>Yurakdan Sevaman W123</title>
</song>